      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FARNCIFUL (2) returns. Couldn't meet market expectation on debut at Newcastle on August 23 but bogged track, so willing to forgive. Looks to have come on nicely during the break, stripping fitter for a trial win on the Beaumont. Gets a key booking in Morgan and looks ready to get off the mark. HELLAVALEGACY (5) also resumes and is another that appears to come on nicely during the break, taking benefit from two hitouts in readiness. Gibbons sticks from the most recent trial. Gets her chance. MAGATAMA (3) was well fancied on debut at Port Macquarie last month but could only manage fifth. She did pull up with excuses when slow to recover, so willing to forgive. SONGBIRD YESSIREE (4) is a Yes Yes Yes filly on debut for the Hopkins team. Has been readied with two soft trials and gets in light with the 3kg claim. Worth monitoring.",
